{"tid":980324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國政府圖利用港資公司獲取敏感衛星技術　美國當局展開調查","createTime":"2019-01-13T12:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T00:01:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1121822578b0ffe6f141f8dcf6561c23a4ce31d9","tid":980324,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/13144745/image1547361841010.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F13144745%2Fimage1547361841010.png&h=c7146ed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國近年大舉發展科技，《華爾街日報》上月曾報道，中國財政部旗下中國東方資產管理公司，通過由有香港護照的商人Charles Yiu Hoi Ying在英屬處女島成立的境外投資企業，向一家和波音公司合作的美國初創企業Global IP注資1.75億美元（約13.65億港元），換取其75%股權，試圖藉此繞過美國對大陸的出口管制，獲取美軍也有使用的敏感衛星技術，波音其後取消和Global IP的衛星訂單。近日該報再有報道指，美國證券交易委員會及商務部正調查波音和Global IP的關係。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，美國證券交易委員會已向Global IP發信，要求公司保留和波音及其他方，包括中國東方的合作文件，認為公司擁有和事件相關的數據。<br />\n<br />\n波音公司沒有對報道發表評論，僅強調公司要採取嚴格措施遵守美國法規。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/267416/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%9C%96%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%B8%AF%E8%B3%87%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%8D%B2%E5%8F%96%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E8%A1%9B%E6%98%9F%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%e3%80%80%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F267416%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%2595%258F%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%25A1%259B%25E6%2598%259F%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593%25e3%2580%2580%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%2F&d=yIH7VtMJPH3CXcSs8ETcl5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=917110f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/267416/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%9C%96%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%B8%AF%E8%B3%87%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E7%8D%B2%E5%8F%96%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E8%A1%9B%E6%98%9F%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%e3%80%80%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B/</a>"},{"pid":"8e403195c6cebd33c5993e87eaca35ffc89b998c","tid":980324,"uid":94828,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:17:56.000Z","msg":"全面禁止香港使用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc5019162b1489a3d08d1c6945cb75d1a3a6236","tid":980324,"uid":52215,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:20:26.000Z","msg":"禁同香港貿易啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c781879bbf0a355d7b9b1766c90efe5f343e49a0","tid":980324,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:40:34.000Z","msg":"搞錯呀，衛星技術中國無咩？使要買人？小香港侮辱國格，應該如何處分？"},{"pid":"63e6c705dd50af805ce1ac7b274980f148c12457","tid":980324,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:41:04.000Z","msg":"應該唔止一單"},{"pid":"ea093b0e4a4cbac14de851e62028371c363a0ada","tid":980324,"uid":35430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T13:45:35.000Z","msg":"關係法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c79aa229f3f3c9a2a867b428995eafd48ad943","tid":980324,"uid":26601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T13:57:42.000Z","msg":"香港關係法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3be472573f8ed58f78ed8327b631c0679f2d28","tid":980324,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T13:58:57.000Z","msg":"香港不嬲係中共間諜, 有咩奇"},{"pid":"daa60fa0559f306010c2766898909e5c571130a4","tid":980324,"uid":48064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T14:00:33.000Z","msg":"香港就快爆煲"},{"pid":"dc8459bbedd009bfc93513095ce38e1582ee8a28","tid":980324,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"姚海鷹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有前科<img src=\"/assets/faces/n